Durban - A taxi driver was rushed to hospital in a critical condition following a shooting at a rank in Mandini, in northern KwaZulu-Natal. IPSS Medical Rescue spokesperson, Paul Herbst, said on Tuesday, they were alerted to the shooting near a Spar in the area. 
 

 

 
 
  
   









